metadata.name: Dark Days, Grey Nights #1/3
metadata.description:
Paulina wearing Bettina Kreb Jewelry and Fernando Boots.

Images were shot on Ilford FP4 Plus black-and-white film with Kiev88 middle format camera in our collectives studio (Fotografie Berlin e.V.). A contact sheet was then developed and scanned. The scan is the basis of this NFT.

The first collector can claim a signed, numbered, and stamped physical contact sheet. Minted in December 2022 by @robcrahmer via manifold.xyz.

ISO 100, 1/250, f/5.6, 40mm  
3800 x 5900 px // 16.4 MB // .png
